				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${\text{tfidf}}\left( {{\text{t}},{\text{d}},{\text{D}}} \right) = tf\left( {t,d} \right) \times {\text{idf}}\left( {{\text{t}},{\text{D}}} \right)$$\end{document}tfidft,d,D=tft,d×idft,D
